{
  "id": "adv_card_chs_52_02",
  "title": "白石千紗",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_kyoto-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "kyoto-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_52_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "夕食までまだ時間があるが\n千紗はどこか行きたい場所はあるのか？",
      "startTime": 3.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_52_02-chs001.m4a",
      "text": "ずっと気になっていた神社に\nこれから行くんです",
      "startTime": 8.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_kyoto-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "kyoto-00-noon",
      "startTime": 10.1000000954
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_52_02-chs002.m4a",
      "text": "そこは歴史のある古い神社で\n『丑の刻参り』で有名な場所なんですよ",
      "startTime": 13.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_kyoto-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "kyoto-00-noon",
      "startTime": 16.9000000954
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_52_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "丑の刻参りって、あの呪いの藁人形の？",
      "startTime": 16.9000000954,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_kyoto-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "kyoto-00-noon",
      "startTime": 22.6000000954
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_52_02-chs003.m4a",
      "text": "はい！　憎い人に見立てた藁人形を\n五寸釘で木に打ちつけて呪いをかける儀式です！",
      "startTime": 26.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_kyoto-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "kyoto-00-noon",
      "startTime": 30.9333334287
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_52_02-chs004.m4a",
      "text": "その神社は昔から丑の刻参りが盛んで、夜な夜な\nコーン、コーンと釘を打つ音が聞こえてきたそうです",
      "startTime": 36.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_52_02-chs005.m4a",
      "text": "大分前に禁止されましたが、もしかしたら今でも\n藁人形に五寸釘を打ち込んでいる人がいるかも……",
      "startTime": 46.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_kyoto-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "kyoto-00-noon",
      "startTime": 50.5000000954
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_52_02-chs006.m4a",
      "text": "もしもそんな人に遭遇したら、完全にホラー映画の\n世界ですよね？　そう思うとぞくぞくしませんか？",
      "startTime": 54.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_kyoto-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "kyoto-00-noon",
      "startTime": 59.1333298683
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_52_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "俺としては、危ない所に行くのは\n止めてほしいんだが……",
      "startTime": 62.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_kyoto-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "kyoto-00-noon",
      "startTime": 64.1666659991
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_52_02-chs007.m4a",
      "text": "心配してくれてありがとうございます\nでも、京都に来たら絶対行くって決めてたんです",
      "startTime": 67.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_52_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "そうか……だが、千紗を一人で行かせるのは心配だ\n俺も一緒に行くよ",
      "startTime": 76.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_kyoto-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "kyoto-00-noon",
      "startTime": 78.2666659991
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_52_02-chs008.m4a",
      "text": "え、はい……それは構いませんけど……\n{user}さんは心配性ですね",
      "startTime": 82.6666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5100.000000000008,
          "startTime": 87.7666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shrine-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shrine-00-noon",
      "startTime": 87.1833316485
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shrine-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shrine-00-noon",
      "startTime": 87.1833316485
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_52_02-chs009.m4a",
      "text": "ここが丑の刻参りで有名な神社なんですね\n確かに神秘的な雰囲気を感じます",
      "startTime": 93.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shrine-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shrine-00-noon",
      "startTime": 97.7999942462
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_52_02-chs010.m4a",
      "text": "こういう場所で罰当たりなことをして、呪われたり\n祟られたりするのはホラー映画のあるあるですよね",
      "startTime": 102.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shrine-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shrine-00-noon",
      "startTime": 106.4999871254
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_52_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "ウキウキした顔で、呪われるとか祟られるとか\n怖いことを言わないでくれ",
      "startTime": 109.7999928792,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_52_02-chs011.m4a",
      "text": "そんなに不安がらなくても大丈夫ですよ",
      "startTime": 112.0666507403,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 8443.3492597,
          "startTime": 120.51
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shrine-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shrine-00-noon",
      "startTime": 115.5999830563
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_52_02-chs012.m4a",
      "text": "神社を参拝する時のルールをちゃんと守れば\nそうそう祟られるなんてことは……ああっ！",
      "startTime": 119.0999984741,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shrine-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shrine-00-noon",
      "startTime": 121.7666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_52_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "えっ？　急に大声を上げて、どうしたんだ？",
      "startTime": 123.1666492144,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_52_02-chs013.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん……\n今、鳥居の下を素通りしましたよね？",
      "startTime": 128.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shrine-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shrine-00-noon",
      "startTime": 133.0999779701
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_52_02-chs014.m4a",
      "text": "お姉ちゃんが言ってました。神社の鳥居をくぐる時は\nお辞儀をして神様に挨拶しなきゃいけないんです",
      "startTime": 138.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shrine-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shrine-00-noon",
      "startTime": 142.3999779701
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_52_02-chs015.m4a",
      "text": "挨拶しないで鳥居をくぐったりしたら\nもしかしたら祟られちゃうかも……",
      "startTime": 146.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shrine-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shrine-00-noon",
      "startTime": 149.9666446368
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_52_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "なんだって！？　いや、だが、祟られるなんて……\nさすがにそんな大事には……",
      "startTime": 153.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_52_02-chs016.m4a",
      "text": "とにかく、これ以上神様を怒らせないように\nきちんとルールを守って参拝するんです",
      "startTime": 160.5000223796,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shrine-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shrine-00-noon",
      "startTime": 163.7000003497
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_52_02-chs017.m4a",
      "text": "まずは手水できちんと手を清めて、お賽銭を入れて\nそれから二礼二拍手一礼をして、お参りをしましょう",
      "startTime": 169.0333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_water-02.m4a",
          "delay": 6900.0000000000055,
          "startTime": 175.9333333333
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_money-01.m4a",
          "delay": 13599.999999999995,
          "startTime": 182.6333333333
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_money-01.m4a",
          "delay": 13266.666666700019,
          "startTime": 182.3
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_52_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "わ、分かった。まずは手を清めて……お賽銭か……\n神様に許してもらうためにも、ここは心持ち多めに……",
      "startTime": 179.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shrine-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shrine-00-noon",
      "startTime": 183.5999922116
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_52_02-chs018.m4a",
      "text": "ああっ！　そんな……なんてことを……\n今、賽銭箱に五百円玉を入れましたよね？",
      "startTime": 188.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shrine-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shrine-00-noon",
      "startTime": 193.6666588783
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_52_02-chs019.m4a",
      "text": "お姉ちゃんが言ってました。五百円玉は縁起が悪いから\nお賽銭に使うのはタブーなんです！",
      "startTime": 198.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shrine-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shrine-00-noon",
      "startTime": 201.7666588783
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_52_02-chs020.m4a",
      "text": "「これ以上大きな硬貨（効果）がない」という意味に\nなるからって……これにはきっと神様もお怒りです！",
      "startTime": 205.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
